Author: portraitofalady87
Text: You *feel* chonky. Objectively you will not be. Semantics, i know - but playing with words was one way I was able to figuratively dissect my brain and figure out how to combat these thoughts. Sorry you feel bad - mine hit overweight for the first time in my life! So Im definitley chonky, but dont feel it yet ðŸ˜‚ anti depressants are working.
